---
---

<section class="relative pt-40 pb-32 px-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[90vh] bg-[#FDFDFD] overflow-hidden">
  <!-- subtle background blur -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-neutral-100 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none opacity-50"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-100 border border-neutral-200 mb-8">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-black"></span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium tracking-wider text-neutral-600 uppercase">Psicología & Alto Rendimiento</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-light tracking-tighter text-neutral-900 mb-8 leading-[1.05]">
      Claridad mental.<br/>
      <span class="font-semibold text-black">Rendimiento absoluto.</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-500 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
      Combino evidencia científica, tecnología de punta y herramientas prácticas para ayudarte a alcanzar tu máximo potencial — en el deporte, en tu carrera y en tu vida.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
      <a href="#agendar" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium bg-black text-white rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <span class="relative z-10">Agendar Hora</span>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-800 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out"></div>
      </a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-neutral-900 hover:text-neutral-600 transition-colors">
        Ver Servicios →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-neutral-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
